item.title: GPX Track Viewer Privacy
item.description: The policy applies to all information collected GPX Track Viewer app for iPhone and any other devices and platforms. Information Collection and Use Your privacy is critically important to us. Therefore GPX Track Viewer does not collect any personally identifiable information from its users, whether directly or by use of third party services and/or libraries. All data processed, edited, created, or in any other way manipulated by the App is never copied, transferred, or otherwise made available to me through means provided by the App.
